<p>[The letter by Charles Darwin, dated 10 December 1872, is in the third person and his wife Emma’s handwriting: it thanks Mr Topham for his suggestion which Darwin “will attend [to] in any future edition”.]<ref target="#foot.f1"/></p> 
                </div>
